      <file type="DATAVERSE-CREATE" purpose="layer2-prompt-c1-reserved">sprk_analysisaction[INS-L2X] id a0e7ac19-cc5e-f111-a825-70a8a59455f4 (carries migrated outcome-extraction.v1.txt content)</file>
