    </files-modified>

    <dataverse-changes>
      <row action="UPDATED" code="INS-AGNT" name="Insights — Agent Service Synthesis" content-version="v1-full-replacement">Pre-C2: Wave B placeholder JPS skeleton. Post-C2: full predict-matter-cost-synthesis.v1.txt migrated into JPS shape with 7 non-negotiable rules, template placeholders {{liveFacts}}/{{cohortObservations}}/{{precedents}} preserved, output schema (value.raw.estimatedTotalCost.{p25,p50,p75} + duration quartiles + confidence + evidence[]≥12 + reasoning) matches .txt exactly.</row>
