    </quality-gates>

    <deploy-implications>
      <bff-redeploy>NOT required — Wave C2 makes Dataverse data changes only; no BFF code changed. The .txt files remain on disk + IngestOrchestrator continues to read them via IInsightsPromptLoader.</bff-redeploy>
