      <c1-deploy-unblocked>Wave C1's deferred Deploy-Playbook.ps1 run is now PARTIALLY UNBLOCKED for Dataverse — the 4 NEW INS-* rows that the universal-ingest@v1 JSON references exist. BFF code redeploy still pending per bff-extensions §F.4 owner-coordinated window.</c1-deploy-unblocked>
    </deploy-implications>

